#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.83"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.83:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.83:0.2"
msgid "9. Macalavagga"
msgstr "9. Confirmed"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: avaṇṇasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.83:0.3"
msgid "83. Avaṇṇārahasutta"
msgstr "83. Where Criticism Takes You"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.83:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Catūhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye."
msgstr "“Mendicants, someone with four qualities is cast down to hell."

msgctxt "an4.83:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.83:1.3"
msgid "Ananuvicca apariyogāhetvā avaṇṇārahassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, "
msgstr ""
"Without examining or scrutinizing, they praise those deserving of criticism, "

msgctxt "an4.83:1.4"
msgid "ananuvicca apariyogāhetvā vaṇṇārahassa avaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, "
msgstr "and they criticize those deserving of praise. "

msgctxt "an4.83:1.5"
msgid ""
"ananuvicca apariyogāhetvā appasādanīye ṭhāne pasādaṃ upadaṃseti, ananuvicca "
"apariyogāhetvā pasādanīye ṭhāne appasādaṃ upadaṃseti—"
msgstr ""
"They arouse faith in things that are dubious, and they don’t arouse faith in "
"things that are inspiring."

msgctxt "an4.83:1.6"
msgid ""
"imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ "
"niraye."
msgstr "Someone with these four qualities is cast down to hell."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.83:2.1"
msgid ""
"Catūhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ sagge."
msgstr "Someone with four qualities is raised up to heaven."

msgctxt "an4.83:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.83:2.3"
msgid "Anuvicca pariyogāhetvā avaṇṇārahassa avaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, "
msgstr ""
"After examining and scrutinizing, they criticize those deserving of "
"criticism, "

msgctxt "an4.83:2.4"
msgid "anuvicca pariyogāhetvā vaṇṇārahassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, "
msgstr "and they praise those deserving of praise. "

msgctxt "an4.83:2.5"
msgid "anuvicca pariyogāhetvā appasādanīye ṭhāne appasādaṃ upadaṃseti "
msgstr "They don’t arouse faith in things that are dubious, "

msgctxt "an4.83:2.6"
msgid "anuvicca pariyogāhetvā pasādanīye ṭhāne pasādaṃ upadaṃseti—"
msgstr "and they do arouse faith in things that are inspiring."

msgctxt "an4.83:2.7"
msgid ""
"imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ "
"sagge”ti."
msgstr "Someone with these four qualities is raised up to heaven.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.83:2.8"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
